sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant FE as Angular
    participant GW as Gateway YARP
    participant BE as Writer BE
    participant RC as rag_client
    participant RAG as rag-service
    participant OAI as OpenAI

    FE->>GW: POST /apps/writer/api/chat Bearer JWT ve conversation_id
    GW->>BE: Bearer iletir
    BE->>BE: optional_user JWT decode user_id cikarir
    BE->>RC: retrieve user_id conv_id son user mesaji
    RC->>RC: internal JWT uret 60s TTL
    RC->>RAG: POST /api/retrieve Bearer ile
    RAG->>RAG: query embed top-k cosine arama
    RAG-->>RC: chunks listesi
    RC-->>BE: chunks
    BE->>BE: context formatla citation listesi kur
    BE->>OAI: stream system prompt ve context ile
    loop tokenlar
        OAI-->>BE: chunk
        BE-->>FE: data satiri token ile
    end
    BE-->>FE: sources event citations dizisi ile
    BE-->>FE: data DONE isareti
